_chathead.png?f4380 1.5x, /images/thumb/Cabin_boy_Jenkins_chathead.png/52px-Cabin_boy_Jenkins_chathead.png?f4380 2x\" data-file-width=\"65\" data-file-height=\"87\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Cabin_boy_Jenkins\" title=\"Cabin boy Jenkins\">Cabin boy Jenkins</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Elvarg\" title=\"Elvarg\">Elvarg</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\">Crandor Wizards</td><td class=\"navbox-list\">\n<ul><li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Melzar_the_Mad\" title=\"Melzar the Mad\"><img alt=\"Melzar_the_Mad chathead.png: Chat head image of Melzar_the_Mad\" src=\"/images/thumb/Melzar_the_Mad_chathead.png/35px-Melzar_the_Mad_chathead.png?3f44f\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"35\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/Melzar_the_Mad_chathead.png/54px-Melzar_the_Mad_chathead.png?3f44f 1.5x, /images/thumb/Melzar_the_Mad_chathead.png/71px-Melzar_the_Mad_chathead.png?3f44f 2x\" data-file-width=\"103\" data-file-height=\"102\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Melzar_the_Mad\" title=\"Melzar the Mad\">Melzar</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Lozar\" title=\"Lozar\">Lozar</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Thalzar</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\">Melzar's Maze</td><td class=\"navbox-list\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/w/Ghost_(Melzar%27s_Maze)\" title=\"Ghost (Melzar&#39;s Maze)\">Ghost</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Lesser_demon_(Melzar%27s_Maze)\" title=\"Lesser demon (Melzar&#39;s Maze)\">Lesser demon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Skeleton_(Melzar%27s_Maze)\" title=\"Skeleton (Melzar&#39;s Maze)\">Skeleton</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Zombie_(Melzar%27s_Maze)\" title=\"Zombie (Melzar&#39;s Maze)\">Zombie</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Zombie_rat\" title=\"Zombie rat\">Zombie rat</a></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\">Items</td><td class=\"navbox-list navbox-parent\" style=\"padding:0\"><table class=\"navbox-subgroup nowraplinks\" data-expandtext=\"show\" data-collapsetext=\"hide\"><tbody><tr class=\"navbox-group navbox-group-split\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title-hidden\" colspan=\"0\" style=\"display:none\"></td><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"navbox-list\">\n<ul><li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Map_part\" title=\"Map part\"><img alt=\"Map part (Melzar).png\" src=\"/images/Map_part_%28Melzar%29.png?ed6d0\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"20\" height=\"21\" data-file-width=\"20\" data-file-height=\"21\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Map_part\" title=\"Map part\">Map Parts</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Crandor_map\" title=\"Crandor map\"><img alt=\"Crandor map.png\" src=\"/images/Crandor_map.png?5352a\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"29\" height=\"27\" data-file-width=\"29\" data-file-height=\"27\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Crandor_map\" title=\"Crandor map\">Crandor map</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Anti-dragon_shield\" title=\"Anti-dragon shield\"><img alt=\"Anti-dragon shield.png\" src=\"/images/Anti-dragon_shield.png?0b6b6\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"27\" height=\"29\" data-file-width=\"27\" data-file-height=\"29\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Anti-dragon_shield\" title=\"Anti-dragon shield\">Anti-dragon shield</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Elvarg%27s_head\" title=\"Elvarg&#39;s head\"><img alt=\"Elvarg&#39;s head.png\" src=\"/images/Elvarg%27s_head.png?c85b3\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"30\" height=\"28\" data-file-width=\"30\" data-file-height=\"28\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Elvarg%27s_head\" title=\"Elvarg&#39;s head\">Elvarg's head</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\">Keys</td><td class=\"navbox-list\">\n<ul><li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Maze_key\" title=\"Maze key\"><img alt=\"Maze key.png\" src=\"/images/Maze_key.png?23ebf\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"28\" height=\"27\" data-file-width=\"28\" data-file-height=\"27\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Maze_key\" title=\"Maze key\">Maze</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Key_(Melzar%27s_Maze)\" title=\"Key (Melzar&#39;s Maze)\"><img alt=\"Key (magenta).png\" src=\"/images/Key_%28magenta%29.png?fe454\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"28\" height=\"27\" data-file-width=\"28\" data-file-height=\"27\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Key_(Melzar%27s_Maze)\" title=\"Key (Melzar&#39;s Maze)\">Coloured</a></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\">Locations</td><td class=\"navbox-list\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/w/Champions%27_Guild\" title=\"Champions&#39; Guild\">Champions' Guild</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Melzar%27s_Maze\" title=\"Melzar&#39;s Maze\">Melzar's Maze</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Crandor\" title=\"Crandor\">Crandor</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Crandor_and_Karamja_Dungeon\" title=\"Crandor and Karamja Dungeon\">Crandor and Karamja Dungeon</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\">Music</td><td class=\"navbox-list\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/w/Attack_2\" title=\"Attack 2\">Attack 2</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/The_Maze\" title=\"The Maze\">The Maze</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Dangerous_Road\" title=\"Dangerous Road\">Dangerous Road</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/The_Shadow\" title=\"The Shadow\">The Shadow</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\">Related</td><td class=\"navbox-list\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/w/Dragon_Slayer_I/Quick_guide\" title=\"Dragon Slayer I/Quick guide\">Quick Guide</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Lady_Lumbridge\" title=\"Lady Lumbridge\">Lady Lumbridge</a></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nParsed by mediawiki‐67df7655d‐7qtxl\nCached time: 20220421171753\nCache expiry: 86400\nReduced expiry: false\nComplications: []\n[SMW] In‐text annotation parser time: 0.001 seconds\nCPU time usage: 0.079 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.101 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 343/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 25011/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 820/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/100\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.012/10.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 937030/367001600 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   44.695      1 -total\n 78.53%   35.101      3 Template:Navbox\n 54.35%   24.293      1 Template:Dragon_Slayer_I\n 31.71%   14.175      1 Template:External\n 13.17%    5.888      1 Template:FromGame\n 13.15%    5.876      9 Template:Chatl\n 11.96%    5.347      2 Template:Ctg\n  5.28%    2.361      6 Template:Plink\n  3.48%    1.556      1 Template:QGLink\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key en_osrswiki:pcache:idhash:71122-0!canonical and timestamp 20220421171753 and revision id 13980647. Serialized with PHP.\n -->\n</div>","rawContent":"{{External|rs}}\n'''Thalzar''' was one of a trio of wizards to escape [[Crandor]] after [[Elvarg]] laid waste to the island. He, [[Lozar]] and [[Melzar the Mad|Melzar]] (of whom Melzar is the last survivor, later to be killed by the adventurer) each took a piece of the [[Crandor map]], in the hope of preventing others from journeying there. It is assumed Thalzar died peacefully - his [[Map parts|third of the map]] is found in a sealed room in the [[Dwarven Mine]], and the [[Oracle]] is now charged with ensuring only those strong enough to defeat Elvarg are given access to Thalzar's map piece.\n\nDuring the [[Dragon Slayer I]] [[Quests|quest]], players will encounter an engraving from Thalzar on the lid of the chest containing one of the map pieces. It makes brief mention of the events on Crandor and asks the player to reconsider taking the map piece within.\n\n==Thalzar's message==\n{{FromGame}}\nHere I rest the map to my beloved home. To whoever finds it, I beg of you, let it be. I was honour-bound not to destroy the map piece, but I have used all my magical skill to keep it from being recovered.\n\nThis map leads to the lair of the beast that destroyed my home, devoured my family, and burned to a cinder all that I love. But revenge would not benefit me now, and to disturb this beast is to risk bringing its wrath down upon another land.\n\nI cannot stop you from taking this map piece now, but think on this: if you can slay the Dragon of Crandor, you are a greater hero than my land ever produced. There is no shame in backing out now.\n\n{{Dragon Slayer I}}\n[[Category:Characters that do not appear in-game]]"}